OL,5, They were the trailblazers of women's  
OL,6, rights in Afghanistan. They were the   
OL,7, staunch defenders of the law, seeking  
OL,8, justice for their country's most       
OL,9, marginalised. But now, more than 220   
OL,10, female Afghan judges are in hiding due 
OL,11, to fear of retribution under Taliban   
OL,12, rule. Six former female judges spoke to
OL,13, the BBC from secret locations across   
OL,14, Afghanistan. All of their names have   
OL,15, been changed for their safety.         
OL,17,FThroughout her career as a judge,      
OL,18,FMasooma has convicted hundreds of men  
OL,19,Ffor violence against women, including  
OL,20,Frape, murder and torture.              
